comments: Avdija (WAS) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
At the end of the drive, Poole (WAS) grabs and restricts Bridges's (BKN) arm, affecting his SQBR and causing him to lose control of the ball.
Claxton (BKN) cleanly blocks the shot attempt prior to when the ball reaches its apex.
Poole (WAS) moves to defend Johnson (BKN) and marginal body contact occurs prior to Johnson releasing the pass.
Claxton (BKN) and Poole (WAS) briefly come together as Poole moves to defend Johnson (BKN) and marginal contact occurs.
Avdija (WAS) brushes Johnson's (BKN) left arm and marginal contact occurs during the shot attempt near the rim.

The crew utilizes instant replay for a potential clear path foul. After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that Poole (WAS) initiates illegal body contact with Dinwiddie (BKN) after he releases the pass to Bridges (BKN) and while there is no defender between Bridges and the basket.
Couilbaly (WAS) makes contact with the ball while simultaneous incidental contact occurs with Bridges' (BKN) right arm.
Poole (WAS) initiates contact with Bridges' (BKN) left arm that affects his SQBR.
Poole (WAS) grabs and holds Dinwiddie's (BKN) left arm as he attempts to get to the pass. The contact occurs after release of the in-bounds pass.
